           struct TagItem *);

   FUNCTION
       Applies HTTA_* tags.  See amihttp.library/tags.

   INPUTS
       txn  - HttpTransaction handle.
       tags - TagItem list.

   RESULT
       success - TRUE (1) or FALSE (0).

   SEE ALSO
       SetHttpTransactionAttrs(), amihttp.library/tags

amihttp.library/SetHttpTransactionAttrs   amihttp.library/SetHttpTransactionAttrs

   NAME
       SetHttpTransactionAttrs -- Variadic transaction configuration.  (V1)

   SYNOPSIS
       success = SetHttpTransactionAttrs(txn, Tag1, ...);

       LONG SetHttpTransactionAttrs(struct HttpTransaction *, ULONG, ...);

   FUNCTION
       Variadic wrapper for SetHttpTransactionAttrsA().

   SEE ALSO
