       D0                                  A0   A1

       STRPTR HttpTransactionRespHeader(struct HttpTransaction *, STRPTR);

   FUNCTION
       Case-insensitive lookup of a response header value.  Pointer valid
       until DisposeHttpTransaction().

   INPUTS
       txn  - HttpTransaction after Perform.
       name - header name (e.g. "Content-Type").

   RESULT
